
There is a white dragon and a red dragon.\nOne day, the white dragon goes to see a computer genius who has built a supercomputer that can simulate realities in a really amazing way.\nThe white dragon is impressed with the computer, but it has no password, so the red dragon comes along and tries to get in.\nThe red dragon is really scared, but he goes in anyway, and finds himself in a really cool place.\nHe really likes it there, but then he gets stuck.\nThen the white dragon comes back and destroys the computer because it was broken.

